reviewText: great movie but some picytures  were unclear
I thought the I have seen all of the Spaghetti Westerns, but, I just found out that I have not.  I love it.

I enjoyed both Volumes 1 and 2, I do wish all the films were Anamophic and wished that DJANGO THE AVENGER had its actual title DJANGO THE BASTARD on screen but that's minor quibs, for the price and at 6 films a set quite reasonable and not bad starter sets for the newbies to the Spaghetti Western family!!!!
the dvd is a clear and crisp transfer to dvd but with minor glitches from the original copy. Even had a scene where an original italian language is spoken then changed back to dubbed english.
OK for what it is and the price.
My father loves it. Many great movies
Just what i expected. Which wasn't a whole lot.  Btw strangers gundown is in this set.  Great campe
